# Project Overview

This is a Next.js project using React and Tailwind CSS. The project follows a modern React application structure with the following key directories:

## Main Directories
- [src/pages](mdc:src/pages) - Next.js pages and routing
- [src/components](mdc:src/components) - Reusable React components
- [src/styles](mdc:src/styles) - Global styles and Tailwind configuration
- [src/lib](mdc:src/lib) - Utility functions and shared logic
- [src/data](mdc:src/data) - Data files and content
- [src/images](mdc:src/images) - Image assets

## Key Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [jsconfig.json](mdc:jsconfig.json) - JavaScript configuration for the project

## Technology Stack
- Next.js 13
- React 18
- Tailwind CSS
- MDX for content
- HeadlessUI for UI components
